FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our food delivery service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the food delivery process work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Simply browse restaurants, select your items, place your order, and track it in real-time. Our drivers will deliver your food right to your doorstep.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Delivery fees vary based on distance and restaurant. The exact fee will be displayed before you complete your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How long does delivery usually take?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times typically range from 30-45 minutes, depending on the restaurant's preparation time and delivery distance.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I schedule an order for later?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, you can schedule orders up to a week in advance. Simply choose the 'Schedule for Later' option during checkout.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if there's an issue with my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: If you experience any problems with your order, please contact our customer support team through the app or website. We're here to help!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food delivery app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants, allowing you to browse menus, place orders, and have food delivered straight to your door. Simply select your items, choose a delivery time, and track your order in real-time.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Delivery fees vary depending on the restaurant and your location. The exact fee will be displayed before you confirm your order. We also offer a subscription service for frequent users that provides free delivery on eligible orders.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How long does delivery usually take?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Delivery times typically range from 30-45 minutes, depending on the restaurant's preparation time and your distance from the eatery. You can always check the estimated delivery time before placing your order.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I customize my order or make special requests?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! Most restaurants allow for customization options within the app. You can also add special instructions for your order in the designated field before checkout. We'll do our best to accommodate your requests.
